Gold Torrent Inc.


            
            Gold Torrent, Inc. engages in the acquisition and ownership of late-stage exploration to development-stage gold mining projects and royalty or streaming interests in low capital intensity and late-stage mining projects in North America. The company was founded on August 15, 2006 and is headquartered in Boise, ID.

            
